  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110105536844\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110105536844\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\">[중이염의 한방치료]&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cd2d9acc1a0b3207.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"422\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:550px; rheight:422px;\" id=\"20110325_191/isuhani_13010327104536IIzT_JPEG/ear.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A2CD294C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cd2d9acc1a0b3207.jpg\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; COLOR: #404040; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림\">삼출성 중이염</span></b></p>\n<p><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; COLOR: #404040; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림\"></span></b><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 굴림; font-size: 10pt;\">Otitis media with effusion<!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /--><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></i></p>\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></i></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 9.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 굴림; font-size: 10pt;\">삼출성 중이염이란 통증이나 발열 등의 급성 증상이 없이<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>중이강 내에 삼출액이 고이는 중이염의 일종으로 이는 장액성 중이염<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">serous otitis media</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>점액성 중이염<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">mucoid otitis media</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\">, Glue ear, Middle ear diffusion </span>등의 동의어로 불리기도 한다.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 9.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 굴림; font-size: 10pt;\">항생제의 사용이 빈번한 최근에 오히려 그 빈도는 높아져 유소아에서의 가장 흔한 청력장애의 원인이 되고 있다.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 9.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 굴림; font-size: 10pt;\">삼출액이 중이강 안에 고여 있는 기간이 약<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 12 </span>주를 경과하면 만성<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">chronic</span></i>으로 생각한다. <span lang=\"EN-US\">(Bluestone, 1984). </span>소아의<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 20~50%</span>가<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 3~10</span>세 사이에 한 번쯤은 이환되는 것으로 많은 연구들에서 보고하고 있다.<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Fiellau-Nikolajsen, 1983). <!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 9.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">1.<span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림\">병 인 <span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></b></p>\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">이관의 기능장애가 중이강의 환기 장애를 일으켜 중이강은 음압상태로 되고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>이 음압상태가 지속되면 고막은 내측으로 함몰되고 중이점막에서는 삼출액이 분비되어 고이게 된다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>이러한 이관 기능의 장애를 일으키는 원인으로는 </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">① 급성 상기도염<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>② 알레르기<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>③ 아데노이드 증식증<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">④ 만성 부비동염<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>⑤ 구개열 등으로 인한 이관개방의 장애<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>⑥ 종양<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>⑦ 재발성 화농성 중이염<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">⑧ 급격한 기압의 변화<span lang=\"EN-US\"> (barotraumas), </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>⑨ 전신적 요소<span lang=\"EN-US\"> (</span>갑상선 기능저하증<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>당뇨병<span lang=\"EN-US\">) </span>등이 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110325_294/isuhani_1301032726424gknWd_JPEG/otitis_media_with_effusion__narmal.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"316\" height=\"159\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:316px; rheight:159px;\" id=\"20110325_294/isuhani_1301032726424gknWd_JPEG/otitis_media_with_effusion__narmal.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A2CD294C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110325_294/isuhani_1301032726424gknWd_JPEG/otitis_media_with_effusion__narmal.jpg?type=w3\"></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">2.<span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림\">진 단<span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 굴림; font-size: 10pt;\">삼출성 중이염은 급성 증상이 없으므로 조기 진단이 어려울 수 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>난청 증상과 고막소견<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>그리고 청력검사 등으로 진단한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 돋움; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 돋움; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">(1)</span><span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 돋움; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 돋움; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">임상양상<span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></b></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">TV </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">소리를 크게 높여 듣는다든지<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>수업 중 주의산만 등의 청력장애의 신호가 될 수 있으며<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>학교에서의 정기 신체검사에서 우연히 발견되기도 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 돋움; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 돋움; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 돋움; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">(2)</span><span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 돋움; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 돋움; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">이학적 검사<span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></b></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 굴림; font-size: 10pt;\">이학적 검사로는<span lang=\"EN-US\"> pneumatic otoscopy </span>가 가장 중요하게 이용되며 고막의 가동성 감소와 다음과 같은 특징적인 고막소견을 관찰할 수 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 58pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">① 내함<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">retraction</span></i>되어 광택소실</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 58pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">② 황갈색<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">amber color</span></i>이나 회백색 혼탁<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>석회 침착<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>반흔성 비후</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 58pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">③ 추골 단돌기의 돌출</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 58pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">④ 추골병이 짧아져 보임 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 58pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">⑤ 삼출액선<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">fluid level</span></i>이나 기포</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 굴림; font-size: 10pt;\">성인에서 특히 일측성 삼출성 중이염이 있는 경우에는 비인강검사<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>경부촉진 등을 반드시 시행하여 이관의 구강 입구부 주위의 종괴 유무를 확인하여야 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 돋움; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 돋움; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">(3)</span><span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 돋움; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 돋움; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">청력 검사<span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></b></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 굴림; font-size: 10pt;\">청력검사상 초기에는 유동적이고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>고음역의 장애가 크나 점차 수평형으로<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 10~40 dB</span>의 전음성 난청소견을 보인다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>임피던스 청력검사<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">impedance audiometry</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span>상 저항의 증가 및 고실도에서<span lang=\"EN-US\"> tympanogram B </span>혹은<span lang=\"EN-US\"> C</span>형을 나타낸다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>대부분의 소아 중이염 환아에서 정상적인 와우기능을 가지고 있는 경우가 많으며 기초적인 확인 자료로서 청력검사가 필요하다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>재발성<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>지속성의 중이염이나 청력감소가 의심되는 경우에는 조기에 검사 및 처치를 필요로 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 돋움; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 돋움; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">(4)</span><span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 돋움; font-size: 10pt;\">고막천자 <span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #404040; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 38pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: 굴림; font-size: 10pt;\">고막천자를 통한 삼출액의 확인으로 진단하기도 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>또한 삼출성 중이염에서는 급성 중이염과 유사한 원인균을 발견할 수 있으며 삼출액 모두에서 균 동정이 가능하지만 농성인 경우가 다른 경우보다 확률이 높다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>: 이상 '일차진료를 위한 이비인후과학임상' 에서 발췌</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">이수한의원에 내원하는 아이들 중에는 삼출성 중이염으로 2달 이상 소아과 치료를 받다가</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">, 좋아지지 않아서 수술을 하자는 얘기를 듣고 수술을 피해보고자 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">내원하는 경우가 있습니다.</span></p><p><br /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">삼출성 중이염은 한방치료로 효과를 잘 보는 질환 중 하나입니다.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">한방치료를 하면 짧게는 2-3주 안에, 자꾸 재발했었거나 면역력이 약해 스스로의 치유력이 많이 떨어진 소아의 경우에는 3개월 정도에 깨끗하게 치료가 됩니다. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">중이염이 1년에 몇차례 재발하거나, 한번 생긴 중이염이 잘 없어지지 않을 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">때엔 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">이수한의원으로 문의하세요.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110325_210/isuhani_1301033735296xMov5_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:193px; rheight:48px;\" id=\"20110325_210/isuhani_1301033735296xMov5_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A2CD294C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110325_210/isuhani_1301033735296xMov5_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w3\"></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
